name: MXHistogramBucket
desc: An object representing a bucket of data in a histogram.

items.name: var bucketStart: Measurement<UnitType>
items.desc: The value of the starting measurement for the bucket.

items.name: var bucketEnd: Measurement<UnitType>
items.desc: The value of the ending measurement for the bucket.

items.name: var bucketCount: Int
items.desc: An integer representing the number of samples in the bucket.
